      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CASH IN COLOUR (2) has missed the frame at his last two but did run well three back when third (23.68) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Better than latest and can atone here. PANAMA ROAD (3) showed good pace and scored by a space (20.19) off a middle draw two back then drew the inside last time and could manage only a half a length 2nd at Grafton (20.13). Bold showing expected. SLIMY TROUT (1) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing eighth (20.59) last time in a Grade 5 at Grafton. Has a good record here at this journey. Leading chance. MEG'S GIRL (7) picked up an unexpected cheque last time and is in the mix again.",
